title: EastEnders.EXTRA.Back.To.Ours.Barbara.Windsor.and.Pam.St.Clement
description:
EastEnders.EXTRA.Back.To.Ours.Barbara.Windsor.and.Pam.St.Clement

Celebrate 30 years of EastEnders in the company of those who know it best - the stars! Relive iconic moments and find out the real gossip from the set.

Barbara and Pat welcome you into their Walford home to celebrate 30 years of EastEnders. Longtime Queen of the Vic is joined by her closest accomplice to review some of their best/worst encounters over the years
